    "html": "<p>I&#39;ve been looking at the submissions in <a href=\"https://expo.getbootstrap.com/\">Bootstrap Expo</a> curated by one of the original <a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/\">Bootstrap</a> developers. And I feel like the Warrior Book needs better design, and I think maybe the Workout Song Generation may benefit from being its own application. In next few weeks, perhaps, I would like to practice art general design and typography for a bit to create something as beautiful as that <a href=\"http://hellohappy.org/beautiful-web-type\">Beautiful Web Type</a> demo.</p>\n"
